			<h4>Contact</h4>
<h1>Get in touch</h1>
<p>If you&#8217;d like a free consultation or have any other queries, <a href="https://calendly.com/andy-garner-elasticmint/30min" target="_blank">book a meeting</a> or send us an <a href="mailto:info@elasticmint.com">email</a>.</p>
<p>We&#8217;re a remote team working with clients across the UK and internationally, offering bespoke software development, technology consultancy, distributed team leadership and fractional CTO services.</p>
<p>Whether you have a defined project in mind, a problem you&#8217;re not yet sure how to solve, or simply want to find out whether Elastic Mint might be a good fit for your organisation, we welcome the conversation. We&#8217;ll give you an honest assessment of whether and how we can help.</p>
<p>Your first call is just a conversation. We&#8217;ll listen to what you&#8217;re trying to do, ask questions to understand the constraints, and only suggest a way forward if we&#8217;re confident we can help. There&#8217;s no hard sell, and we&#8217;re happy to sign an NDA if you want to discuss anything sensitive.</p>
<p>We&#8217;re happy to hear from you whether you have a defined project, are weighing up a tech decision and want a second opinion, are considering a fractional CTO arrangement, or need extra engineering capacity alongside your existing team. The earlier we&#8217;re brought into the conversation, the more useful we tend to be.</p>
<p>We aim to respond to all enquiries within two working days.</p>
